Start
/ Arms the IsExecuting recursion guard end-to-end and asserts on the
/ specific error key — guard surfaces ChannelNotFound, recursion-depth
/ backstop surfaces RecursionDepthExceeded.
- set channel "echo" call EchoBack
- write 'hello' to echo, on error call InspectError
- assert %errorKey% equals 'ChannelNotFound'
